                <h1>Mastering Green Screen in iMovie: A Simple Guide</h1>
                <p>To use green screen on iMovie, first, import your video clips. Place the background clip on the timeline, then drag your green screen video above it. Select the green screen video, click the "Video Overlay Settings" button, and choose "Green/Blue Screen" from the drop-down menu. Adjust as necessary and export your project!</p>
